{"tid":125127,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死4隻]長江南京段船舶爆燃　三船起火釀四死","createTime":"2017-02-18T08:08:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T08:08:52.000Z","uid":32407,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4db27c75fcc5a118d991b6cb74adf5eb7d446b4c","tid":125127,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T08:08:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170218/bkncn-20170218122531084-0218_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170218%2Fbkncn-20170218122531084-0218_05011_001.html&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3mowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=ae2d0126\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170218/bkncn-20170218122531084-0218_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170218/photo/bkncn-20170218122531084-0218_05011_001_01b.jpg?20170218125053\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170218%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170218122531084-0218_05011_001_01b.jpg%3F20170218125053&h=469083f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長江南京段江心洲附近昨晚有三艘船起火，事故船上共有12人，因大火全數落水，其中8人獲救，4人死亡。大火至今日凌晨1時30分才撲滅。目前政府相關部門尚無江水污染報告，事故起因仍有待調查。<br />\n<br />\n據南京市委宣傳部新聞發布官方微博的通告，事發於長江南京水道145號浮標右岸側附近，初步界定為船舶爆燃事故。事發後至今日早上，環保部對事發地區下游飲用水源地進行監測，其中苯系物和油都未被檢出。目前，事發地下游的水廠水質未發生異常，大氣由於短期內燃燒產生的影響很小，隨着火勢的熄滅已消除。<br />\n<br />\n爆炸人民共和國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}